{
  "stem": "1033.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Fellas, come on down, we got a job for you, $30 a week, which was, like, $12 a week more than what we were earning to mind a powerhouse.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So we lived in the bush with a French-Canadian family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't say we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we were there three years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We saved our money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And one day George came in with a Cadillac car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And, and, and I said, I didn't want the car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So we separated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I had $1,800 when I left Mattawa and came to Toronto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I got a job with Ontario Hydro.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And in 1954-- I came to Toronto in '52 from Mattawa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "In '54, on the street, I had a very offensive friend who was bragging-- oh, I shouldn't say this-- about this girl.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I felt sorry about this girl ever-- even before I met her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Anyhow, we got-- we met.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And she loved poetry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And her name was Ruth Levstein.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And after that, this fellow had nothing to brag about because we got married in five weeks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And she gave me three beautiful children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I never looked back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "The rest is history.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And unfortunately, my wife died in 1978.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "She was 43.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And then, of course, I remarried.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And I have an enchanted life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] What a wonderful question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, the first things in Montreal when I came-- when we left-- George and I left Glace Bay and came to Montreal.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And both of us started working in the clothing trade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were-- there were a lot of French Canadians in that trade, working alongside us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of the marvelous, uplifting, astounding discoveries I made-- that the French Roman Catholics were also circumcised.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
